    <div class="user-about">
        <h1 class=" animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">Tech I use</h1>
        <p class="animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">As a developer, I spend countless hours at my desk, so enhancing my workspace for maximum productivity and enjoyment is a priority.</p> <br>
        <p class="animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">Since I started earning, Iâ€™ve invested in better tech to support my goals in professional areas, I'll try to keep this list as updated as possible.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="devices-container animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
      <Device  href='/posts/post-1' name='MateBook 16s(2023)' description='Laptop' />
      <Device  href='/posts/post-7' name='Keychron V1' description='Keyboard' />
      <Device  href='/posts/post-2' name='Nikon D3300' description='Camera' />
